name: Miracle Manfish
description: Come one come all, ladies and gentlemen, brothers and sisters, weirdos and outcasts, step right up, gather round and come a little closer. Let me introduce you to the one and only magnificent, humble, fortune telling, Miracle Manfisch. A most original interactive fusion of art, magic and technology. Befriend the Manfisch and he shall prove an indispensable companion to help you navigate your journey through these uncertain times. Simply connect your faculties to the information super highway and find your way to this page, then all shall be revealed before your very own eyes…
